description:
Please feel free to message Circle Liu on Whatsapp: +61 412 188 023 or Wechat: circleliu_agent to discuss further. Spoken Languages: English, Mandarin and Cantonese.

Your new home is located in the well-known complex of Eastwood Central, with 400 meters to train station, next to plenty of restaurants, close to retail spaces, parks and Eastwood lifestyle hub, including schools and the Eastwood commercial district. Everything you needs is at your door steps.
It features with 2 side by side car space and a huge 100 sqm wrap around balcony with region view for your comfortable living.

You'll love the nice and bright living and dining area with floor to ceiling sliding doors with direct access to the balcony, which allows plenty of natural sunlight into your apartment, and extends the indoor/outdoor space for friends and family gathering.

Main features:
- Open kitchen with stainless Steel Miele appliances
- Premium timber like floors throughout for low maintenance
- Air Conditioning for year around comfort
- Lift access
- Intercom
Strata approx. $1275/q, Water approx. $165/q, Council approx. $325/q
